(z+z^{-1})^{2n}
\cos^{2n}x
\def\i{\mathbf i}z=\exp(\i x)
2^{2n}
  (z+z^{-1})^{2n}=\sum_{k=0}^{2n}\binom{2n}kz^k(z^{-1})^{2n-k}  =\sum_{k=0}^{2n}\binom{2n}kz^{2(k-n)}  =\sum_{k=-n}^n\binom{2n}{n+k}z^{2k}. 
   \cos(x)^{2n}= 2^{-2n}\sum_{k=-n}^n\binom{2n}{n+k}\exp(2\i kx)  = 2^{-2n}\sum_{k=-n}^n\binom{2n}{n+k}\cos(2kx). 
